---
title: Chicken & Mushroom Stroganoff with Potato Mash & Baby Leaves
description: Very few things can beat a dinner that warms you from the inside out. Take this stroganoff, a pillow of golden mashed potato covered with chicken and mushrooms in a creamy tomato-based sauce. It’s guaranteed to leave you feeling full and toasty.
